  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >DEEPLY DARK:FOUND FOOTAGE</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1291660/extras/5a520ba075b7d2dc2eaf4c3f8a4aae6c.poster.avif?t=1705258256\" width=484 height=274 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1291660/extras/5a520ba075b7d2dc2eaf4c3f8a4aae6c.webm?t=1705258256\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1291660/extras/5a520ba075b7d2dc2eaf4c3f8a4aae6c.mp4?t=1705258256\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>The M. E. G. releases this software with interactive recorded material within various levels of the \"Backrooms\" for informational use.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >WARNING</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1291660/extras/22c8163361bb7cfa33125529218209f4.poster.avif?t=1705258256\" width=484 height=274 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1291660/extras/22c8163361bb7cfa33125529218209f4.webm?t=1705258256\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1291660/extras/22c8163361bb7cfa33125529218209f4.mp4?t=1705258256\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>This is not a game, the experiences with this software can be disturbing for some people and there are those who claim that it is cursed because they have found patterns in fatal accidents related to its users, so we cannot guarantee its safety.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >OTHER ENCRYPTED SOFTWARES</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1291660/extras/14ed75991b0e2b717abd73dadb414c63.poster.avif?t=1705258256\" width=484 height=274 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1291660/extras/14ed75991b0e2b717abd73dadb414c63.webm?t=1705258256\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1291660/extras/14ed75991b0e2b717abd73dadb414c63.mp4?t=1705258256\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Along with \"Deeply Dark: Found Footage\" the M. E. G. has found other software that is still encrypted and a specialized group is in charge of deciphering the code to make it public.",
